snippet.title: Rendezvous | Early Alpha Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Rendezvous is a 2.5D pixel art puzzle adventure game where you follow Setyo, an ex-agent living his quiet life only to find her sister getting in trouble in the dystopian futuristic city of Neo-Surabaya.
-
Music by:

Already Evil - Infraction
https://youtu.be/oL11Nvobdaw

Truth Police - Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ISzMKKsbJ60
